channel.title: Website Template
channel.description:
I need a website template :o I would make it myself but I don't got photoshop on this laptop, and it would be hard to make it with no mouse anyways.. If you could make it I would appreciate it ;D
What I want it something like.. Banner ontop, height 300 length 600. I want the main template to be whatever a normal one would be in length and what ever height you think would work, I'm not to sure about sizes atm, I want the navigation to be on the left featuring about 5 buttons, or the space for them, I can make my own later. I want the colors to be black, and neon green as borders, ect. You should know what I'm talking about if you've seen alienware. I want a main info section in the center of the template, should be considerably large but not to big. I would appreciate it if you atleast try to make something, I don't expect it to be done right away. Even if you aren't that good at graphics I would like to see you try to make one, it could help you improve your graphic abilitys.
Many thanks Exe626
